'''Pí-li-sṳ̀ liâng Congo''' (比利時領--, [[Fap-vùn]]: Congo Belge) he [[Pí-li-sṳ̀]] chhai 1908-ngièn chṳ 1960-ngièn chhai kîm-ngit [[Congo Mìn-chú Khiung-fò-koet]] ke [[chhṳ̍t-mìn-thi]]. Chhai 1885-ngièn, [[Êu-chû]] kok-koet kí-hàng liáu [[Berlin Sî-Fî Fi-ngi]]. Tet-koet chṳn-fú chhai Fi-ngi tông-chûng pá Congo kâu yi Pí-li-sṳ̀ koet-vòng [[Leopold 2-sṳ (Pí-li-sṳ̀)|Leopold 2-sṳ]], yî chok-vì khì sṳ̂ ngìn Liâng-thi, pin chiông chṳ̂ chhṳ̂n-vì [[Congo Chhṳ-yù pâng]]. Yì to-liáu 1908-ngièn, kông kó chang-sṳt pûn chón kâu yi Pí-li-sṳ̀ chṳn-fú, pin kói chhṳ̂n-vì Pí-li-sṳ̀ liâng Congo. Yì Congo chui fu shu̍ ke thi-fông - [[Katanga-sén]] ya pûn Pí-li-sṳ̀ kí kâ Kûng-sṳ̂ khiung-thùng khôi-fat liáu. 

Pí-li-sṳ̀ liâng Congo tshìn [[Congo ngùi-kî]] fat-sâng sṳ̀, chhai 1960-ngièn 6-ngie̍t 30-ngit chhí-tet thu̍k-li̍p. Than Pí-li-sṳ̀ chṳn-fú sa yìn lâu [[Zaire]] (kîm Congo Mìn-chú Khiung-fò-koet) pó-chhṳ̀ thi̍t-sû ke kôan-he, yû yit-thin ke chṳn-chhṳ fò kîn-chi sông ke yáng-hióng li̍t.

